=== radiPanel: AutoDJ Control===
Contributors: Matthew Gall (iCame), Robert Clarke (SimplexWebs Ltd)

radiPanel: AutoDJ Control is an extension of the PHP / MySQL powered RadiPanel system developed by Josh under a Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike 2.0 UK: England & Wales Licence (which can be viewed at http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/2.0/uk/), that allows staff to control their CentovaCast powered shoutcast stream (and AutoDJ) from within radiPanel (CastControl coming soon!)

